I am Ukrainian and I want to help with living expenses.

My name is Anatolij, I am from Ukraine and I have been living in Poland for 20 days now. But I still want to help Ukrainian  with their living expenses. So I decided to create this fundraising campaign on GoFundMe.

Please help me from Ukraine !

The crisis in Eastern Ukraine has been going on for a while now. It started when the Ukrainian government tried to change the law that would allow regions to have more autonomy. This proposed law was seen as an act of treason by many people who live in Eastern Ukraine and they started protesting against it. The protests turned into armed conflict when Russia, who is backing these people, sent troops into Eastern Ukraine.

As a result of this conflict, there are many people who need help and support.
